text: Paris Trout is a 1991 American made-for-television drama movie directed by Stephen Gyllenhall and stars Ed Harris, Dennis Hopper, and Barbara Hershey. It is based on 1988 novel of the same name by Pete Dexter. ==Other websites== * * Category:1991 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:Movies about racism Category:Movies about rabies
